{
  "texts": [
    "UniProt 74 sequences containing exactly one Sod_Cu Pfam 75 domain were downloaded.",
    "Hmmsearch (Hmmer, http://hmmer. org/; ref.",
    "76) identified the Sod_Cu domain envelopes.",
    "Sequences were truncated to remove extraneous sequences beyond the bounds of the Sod_Cu match.",
    "Additional quality filtering was performed."
  ]
